 />\n不過佢哋操到個屎忽好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c12c137e87109a7197f163e975eebaf2b6429c6","tid":462192,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T00:57:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>白人多數個輪廓深，中國人，港女 多數 豬膽鼻， 下巴短， 皮膚差，眼小，面圓，仲要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">無波，腳粗</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多數輪廓深=多數靚？</blockquote><br />\n深起碼唔會太醜"},{"pid":"98a77cd16bdb1ab8b80672a6500f7df4af7c5cf4","tid":462192,"uid":55628,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T00:58:25.000Z","msg":"呢個post好似調轉咗"},{"pid":"a96148ec6415233723e385bad9c09c1b22ed8887","tid":462192,"uid":83340,"like":15,"dislike":6,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T01:01:05.000Z","msg":"日本人先最keep得，反而d鬼婆30就下垂巢皮"},{"pid":"65cd998ad1c9c0aa96ebb9691721c313ec91ecfc","tid":462192,"uid":41791,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T01:05:42.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成件事調轉晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n顯到你勁井底蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係又要踩底自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"350aef388047fca2a49c755655265354e7578afd","tid":462192,"uid":41791,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T01:09:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪玩啦樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成件事調轉晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n顯到你勁井底蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係又要踩底自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\nd鬼妹，你以為25咁樣<br />\n點知先得個17歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬼仔仲誇張，17歲已經好似30咁<img src